  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You conjure a Huge construct made of Water &amp; Chakra forming a Huge beast of your description that uses your Ninjutsu attack bonus and Save DC for effects that require it.</p><p>It rolls initiative as it has its own turns, using your Ninjutsu Ability Modifier + Proficiency as its Initiative.</p><p>You can as a bonus action on your turn, so long as you are in physical contact with this construct merge into its head. While you are merged in this way you have total Cover against attacks and other effects outside of the Lion.</p>",
